Relive the age when monsters ruled the skies! Join scientists making astonishing new discoveries about the stunning diversity and complexity of pterosaurs ? the largest creatures ever to take wing!
? Trek from America to Mongolia, Niger and beyond as new finds begin to solve the mystery of how pterosaurs lived, flew, and hunted during their 150 million-year reign..
? See what happens when (computer-animated) pterosaurs meet dinosaurs, as they did millions of years ago.
